# ELK Custer Health APi Commands

<https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/7.9/cluster-health.html>

Cluster GET API

Returns cluster-wide settings. = Non Defaults

GET /_cluster/settings

Returns Cluster wide Settings including Defaults

GET /_cluster/settings?include_defaults

GET _cluster/health/_all

GET _cluster/health?pretty

GET _cat/nodes?v

## Nodes States API

Returns cluster nodes statistics.

Request
GET /_nodes/stats

GET /_nodes/<node_id>/stats

GET/_nodes/stats/<metric>

GET/_nodes/<node_id>/stats/<metric>

GET /_nodes/stats/<metric>/<index_metric>

GET /_nodes/<node_id>/stats/<metric>/<index_metric>
